# IRS Form 990 Field Reference

This document describes every field extracted from the IRS 990 XML schemas, organized by form and schedule. Each entry shows:

- **What it is** (human-readable label and description)
- **Data type** (what kind of value to expect)
- **Where to find it** (xpath in the XML)
- **Which versions** include this field
- **Repeating group**, if the field appears once per entity (e.g., once per officer, once per grant)

---
